Package: melted
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: MLT multi-unit video playout server
 Melted is a GPL multi-unit video playout server with realtime effects,
 built on top of the MLT multimedia framework. It is controlled over the
 network via the MVCP protocol.
 .
 This package contains the melted server, the mvcp command line clients,
 the shared libraries (libmvcp, libmelted, libmelted++) and the MLT
 modules required at runtime.

Package: melted-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends:
 melted (= ${binary:Version}),
 libmlt-dev | libmlt7-dev,
 libmlt++-dev | libmlt++7-dev,
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: MLT video playout server - development files
 Melted is a GPL multi-unit video playout server with realtime effects,
 built on top of the MLT multimedia framework.
 .
 This package contains the headers, pkg-config files and unversioned
 shared library symlinks needed to build software against the melted
 libraries (libmvcp, libmelted, libmelted++).
